{"tid":1162493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門36歲女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-20T02:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T08:03:28.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"724c4272e1f29f2b713aac4ca424cf7d89073303","tid":1162493,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iVkL26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iVkL26.png&h=f0cc72a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BATRSH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBATRSH6.png&h=838b048c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到場調查。張家豪攝<br />\n<br />\n屯門寶田邨2座，凌晨5時許，一名女子從大廈高處墮下，倒地重創昏迷不醒，途人發現報警，救護員趕至現場，惟證實姓繆（36歲）女子已告死亡，警員封鎖現場展開調查。據悉，事主有精神病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ152AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=abf4adac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"5bf1f4ac522e156720fa509cafc15d28d4dc6320","tid":1162493,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:02:25.000Z","msg":"寶田"},{"pid":"b102472f4be580de326348a55872966a7273eeb1","tid":1162493,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebe7080651a248886fa2b2da78fc851058764e2","tid":1162493,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"全屯門區最垃圾嘅公屋應該係寶田邨<br />\n中轉屋，啲單位超細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />精神病人集中地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多支那人<img s